title: Dak Prescott, Browns, Patriots, and where Colin was right & wrong
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Browns, Patriots, and where Colin was right & wrong
description:
Colin gives his thoughts on Cowboys QB Dak Prescott's performance against the Saints, his thoughts on the Browns and QBs like Baker Mayfield, the Patriots win over the Bills, and where he was right and wrong over the weekend. Guests include Eric Mangini, Torry Holt, Trent Dilfer, and Tony Gonzalez.
